# creating orders table and inserting data

CREATE TABLE Orders (
    OrderID INT PRIMARY KEY,
    CustomerName VARCHAR(100),
    OrderDate DATE,
    Amount DECIMAL(10,2)
);

1.creating Index on orderID

CREATE INDEX idx_OrderID
ON Orders(OrderID);

Benefit of an Index
It improves the speed of data retrieval
 (SELECT queries) by allowing the database to find rows faster.